OL,6,FA family came home from a day out to
OL,7,Ffind their home devastated by fire.
OL,9,FNathan Abbott, Katie Craddock and
OL,10,Ftheir four children were at a
OL,11,Ffundraising event on 25 October when
OL,12,Fthey received a phone call from the
OL,13,Ffire brigade.
OL,15,FThey sped home in a taxi to their
OL,16,Ffamily home on Old Road in Hyde, to
OL,17,Ffind it had been destroyed in a fire.
OL,19,FNathan, 32, said: "We've not been able
OL,20,Fto salvage anything, maybe a couple of
OL,21,Fpictures.
