OL,6,FA friend called Katie to say there
OL,7,Fwere three fire engines outside the
OL,8,Fhouse with a ladder up to the window.
OL,10,F"I saw my dog, Teddy, standing in the
OL,11,Froad and I just ran straight over, she
OL,12,Fhad to be resuscitated for 15 minutes,
OL,13,Fbut luckily she's alright," said Katie.
OL,15,FAccording to Nathan, 32, the source of
OL,16,Fthe fire was from a fridge they had
OL,17,Fbought brand new back in 2021.
