OL,6,FNathan said that the event they
OL,7,Fattended was the first time the entire
OL,8,Ffamily had been out of the house in a
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FHe said: "At that time I'd be making
OL,12,Ftea for me and the missus. The kids
OL,13,Fwould be upstairs, it would have
OL,14,Fkilled me instantly. It's a harrowing
OL,15,Fthought."
OL,17,FWith Christmas just around the corner,
OL,18,Fearly presents for the children were
OL,19,Fincinerated and an exciting family
OL,20,Fholiday to Disneyland has now been
OL,21,Fthrown into jeopardy.
