OL,6,F"When we eventually got back inside,
OL,7,Feverything was black, you could just
OL,8,Fsmell smoke," Nathan explained.
OL,10,F"Everything was destroyed, the kitchen
OL,11,Fwas gone. There were some toys in
OL,12,Fthere, a couple outfits and things.
OL,14,F"We were supposed to be going to
OL,15,FDisneyland in January, a lot of the
OL,16,Fstuff we had saved for that has gone
OL,17,Finto this and a lot of the stuff we
OL,18,Fhad bought for that is gone.
